{"tid":1158267,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《紐約時報》報道華裔建築師貝聿銘逝世　終年102歲","createTime":"2019-05-17T00:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T00:04:00.000Z","uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c857ef8fb2004eca92e3728eb84adecc36445b","tid":1158267,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457963-20190517.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457963-20190517.htm&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX5szS%2Fgy1fqSqMk7TcT3QhU%3D&h=f8298b18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457963-20190517.htm&h=3fd3195a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457963-20190517.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美籍華裔建築師貝聿銘逝世，終年102歲。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》引述貝聿銘親屬報道這項消息。<br />\n<br />\n貝聿銘1948年在哈佛大學建築系畢業，進入建築界後，初時大部分時間與美國著名地產商合作，參與多幢摩天建築物設計。<br />\n<br />\n貝聿銘其後參與多間著名博物館設計，包括美國華盛頓國家美術館的東館，以及巴黎<span style=\"color: gold;\">羅浮宮外的玻璃金字塔</span>等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，位於香港中環的<span style=\"color: gold;\">中國銀行大廈</span>，貝聿銘亦有份參與設計。"},{"pid":"381157b88344506b34d1db2931430f6e1caa0ced","tid":1158267,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:04:00.000Z","msg":"push"}]}